<h1 class="title">Creating Android apps using Chicken Scheme</h1>

<main id="outline-container-orgheadline1" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgheadline1"><span class="section-number-2">1</span> Objective</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">
<p>
To setup a toolchain to allow apps to be developed on a linux laptop and run/debug on Android.
</p>
</div>
</main>

<main id="outline-container-orgheadline3" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgheadline3"><span class="section-number-2">2</span> Links and references</h2>
